==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Popularly
<hw>Pop"u*lar*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a popular manner; so as
to be generally favored or accepted by the people; commonly; currently;
<as>as, the story was <ex>popularity</ex> reported</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The victor knight,⟦br⟧
Bareheaded, <qex>popularly</qex> low had bowed.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Popularness</ent>⟦br⟧
